{
  "stem": "25834.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was short, small, and still I was good shooter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And also, the other-- other subject, sport subject, that was the rowing on the skinny boat, eight people plus the fellow who's steering.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was on the top of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was my pleasure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we go sometime from Warsaw up to the stream, 15, 20 kilometers, and back [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was my fabor-- favor sports subject.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's during the academic time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was sometime upset my children was not so good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I wish-- you know, Konrad finished Princeton and Cornell and never was in the-- some sports involvement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's, I think, for young people is very good and a very important thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was my time in the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Generally speaking, I have good relationship, because-- mostly, because I was, all the time, on the top in the high school in sport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody like being friend with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mostly people go to me, not I go to people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would never have special problem with friends, with the professor or something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- maybe, I was not all all that right, and still people try and be friendly with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No problem with a relationship between the students and professor, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was young, was one-- in my class was one Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because mostly was people Catholic and Protestant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe 4 Protestant, not 25, 30 people, and 1 Jewish, Wodka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And young fellow, from poor family, and later, after 14 years, our-- my age, 14, go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This time was Palestine, I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was-- he was, you know, friendly, like, with everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
